### Country Currency Exchange API Tests

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003

### 1. Test Refresh Countries and Save
POST {{baseUrl}}/countries/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get All Countries (after refresh)
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries

###

### 2a. Get Countries filtered by region
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?region=Africa

###

### 2b. Get Countries filtered by currency
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?currency=NGN

###

### 2c. Get Countries sorted by GDP descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?sort=gdp_desc

###

### 2d. Get Countries filtered and sorted
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?region=Africa&currency=NGN&sort=gdp_desc

###

